node.text:
Introducing the @jacobandco Bugatti Chiron Tourbillon Baguette range.

Since 2019, the partnership between Jacob & Co and Bugatti has helped push designs out of this world, creating these never before seen examples.

Jacob & Co have released many different iterations of the Bugatti Chiron Tourbillon; these examples pictured here are the Baguette variations. Which is your favourite?

By: @jacobandco for @bugatti
#millionairesurroundings #jacobandco #bugatti

#chiron #watch #watches #watchesofinstagram #watchcollector #watchaddict #luxury #jewelry

Monday morning meditation in the form of bird created in the sky by 2,200 drones #millionairesurroundings

By: @geoscan.show

#lightshow #dronestagram #drones #drone #dronesdaily #dronevideo #lightshows #mondaymeditation #calming

Assembly of the @jacobandco Twin Turbo Furious finished in Rose Gold 😍

Take a closer look at this phenomenal watch being assembled by the Jacob & Co artisans. With its painstakingly hand-decorated and hand-assembled 832 components, the Twin Turbo Furious is a true Grand Complication Masterpiece that offers a singular combination of ultra-high-end mechanisms, all exclusive to Jacob & Co.

Limited to 18 pieces worldwide, making this one very rare watch.
